; Pinned because @codetrix-studio/capacitor-google-auth@3.4.x declares a
; peer dep on @capacitor/core@^6 but the project runs Capacitor 8 (the
; plugin works fine at runtime — this is a stale peer range). Without
; this, fresh installs on clean build hosts (EC2) blow up with ERESOLVE.
; Remove once we migrate to a plugin with a Capacitor-8 peer range.
legacy-peer-deps=true
